p.k: Lola agrees on pet-sitting the goldfish belonging to Honorine her former neighbor. Of course the Guanos have set their sights on the poor creature and Pat has to keep a close eye on it. Lola finds out that it’s actually her neighbor’s birthday and plans a surprise for her. Meanwhile Pat is led down into the sewers for merciless battle with the Guanos. Our hero has to get his feet wet!
